<h1 class="article__title">A faith-based aid revolution in the Muslim world?</h1>
</div>
</div>
<div class="article__banner">
<figure class="image">
<div class="image__ratio" style="aspect-ratio:300/267;">
<picture>
<source srcset="https://assets.thenewhumanitarian.org/s3fs-public/styles/responsive_large/public/images/2773.jpg.webp?itok=QzPLEAyP 1x, https://assets.thenewhumanitarian.org/s3fs-public/styles/responsive_large_2x/public/images/2773.jpg.webp?itok=bfVB257_ 2x" media="all and (min-width: 75em)" type="image/webp" width="300" height="267" />
<source srcset="https://assets.thenewhumanitarian.org/s3fs-public/styles/responsive_medium/public/images/2773.jpg.webp?itok=9ByRENBQ 1x, https://assets.thenewhumanitarian.org/s3fs-public/styles/responsive_medium_2x/public/images/2773.jpg.webp?itok=fCKUqAdp 2x" media="all and (min-width: 50em)" type="image/webp" width="300" height="267" />
